# Deploy-only workflow

This project is **GitHub Pages only**. Do not set up or rely on local preview.

## After code changes

1. Run `python scripts/sync_content.py generate` only when `data/*.json` changed (CI also runs this).
2. **Always commit and push to `main`** — deployment is triggered by GitHub Actions (`Deploy GitHub Pages`).
3. Do **not** run `python -m http.server`, local `docs/config.js`, or `.env` for verification.
4. Verify on https://rlarlgns-evan.github.io/potato/ after Actions succeeds (hard refresh).

## Secrets & config

- API keys: GitHub Repository Secrets → injected as `docs/config.js` at deploy time.
- Never add `docs/config.js`, `docs/config.example.js`, or `.env` to the repo.
- TourAPI key: `TOUR_API_SERVICE_KEY` in Actions secrets only.

## Cache busting

Bump `?v=N` in `docs/index.html` (style, data, icons, app) when static assets change; increment from current version.

## Local-only files

Do not create or restore: `.devcontainer/`, `.env.example`, local `config.js`, Streamlit, local DB files.
